
Mercurial plugin for Eclipse
============================

This project uses maven. To work on or build the plugin:
1. Install maven
2. Optionally install m2eclipse
3. On the command line in the plugin directory run: 
     $ mvn eclipse:eclipse
     or, if you are building the plugin 
     $ mvn eclipse:eclipse -Declipse.useProjectReferences=false
   If using m2eclipse you can invoke the MercurialEclipse-MavenInit launch in the .settings 
   directory (it should show up automatically in the run configurations list).

